data.description: ***Purchase this condo with a 3.125% interest rate! Seller's FHA loan is ASSUMABLE with the option to use HomeLight's Ultra program. Monthly mortgage payment is under $2,000 + HOA! Inquire here: http://hmlt.co/100-park-ave-w-apt-604*** Come experience luxury city living on your very own corner of Park Avenue West. Sweeping views above the treetops, incredible natural light in all corners of the condo whether you're taking it in from the extra large bedroom, your oversized living room or the covered balcony at sunrise or dusk. Top of the line updates inside, nothing has been forgotten. Over $50,000 in upgrades made to this unit in the last 5 years. Walk into your clean, modern kitchen with matte black finishes, stunning heath tile backsplash, custom kitchen cabinets and sleek white quartz countertops with a waterfall edge. KitchenAid appliances (new in 2021) will all stay. Washer & Dryer added to the unit in 2022. Plank flooring throughout the open living room and bedroom, modern details continue in the updated bathroom with stacked subway tile, the oversized shower and Room & Board vanity. Updated window coverings, light fixtures, hardware, doorknobs and thermostat. Two, tandem parking spots underground and located right by the elevator for convenience and safety. Community amenities are endless: onsite maintenance and management, secure package delivery, 24/7 gym, outdoor pool/hot tub, cabanas and gas grills. For the four-legged residents "100 Bark Ave" features a private dog park and dog wash! The location can't be beat, walking distance to everything Uptown, Downtown, Five Points and Rino have to offer. Schedule your showing today!
